  "instructions": [
    "Heat the olive oil in a large saucepan over medium heat.",
    "Add the chopped onion and cook until it is translucent.",
    "Add the garlic-infused oil, smoked paprika, salt, and black pepper, and cook for 1 minute.",
    "Add the chopped cashew nuts and cook for 2 minutes, stirring frequently.",
    "Add the uncooked white rice and cook for 1 minute, stirring constantly.",
    "Add the vegetable broth and yuzu juice, and bring to a boil.",
    "Reduce the heat to low, cover, and simmer for 18 minutes.",
    "Remove from heat and let it rest for 5 minutes.",
    "Fluff the pilaf with a fork and serve hot."
